com.extjs.gxt.ui.client.fx
Class Effect

java.lang.Object
  com.extjs.gxt.ui.client.fx.Effect
Direct Known Subclasses:
Effect.Blink, Effect.FadeIn, Effect.FadeOut, Effect.Scroll, Effect.SlideIn, Effect.SlideOut
public class Effect
extends java.lang.Object

Effects are a single fx operation involving an element, property, and to / from values.

This code is partially based on code from the MooTools Project by Valerio Proietti.
